g.text: Category : String {Plumbing, Electrical, HVAC, Structural, Other}
Priority : String {Low, Medium, High, Urgent, Emergency}
Status : String {New, InProgress, Completed, Rejected, OnHold, Closed}
RecurrencePattern : String {None, Daily, Weekly, Monthly, Yearly}
NotificationType : String {StatusChange, Assignment, Alert, System, PriorityChange}
- Passwords are stored using industry-standard hashing
- Description must be at least 20 characters
